title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Setting aside your own interests enables you to positively impact your world. Avoid fretting over a dilemma that appears to have no immediate solution. Otherwise, you could keep digging deeper into your own knowledge base to search for your answers and become frustrated when you dont reach pay dirt now. Nevertheless, it may be better to step up to offer aid to someone else today. You might find their problem mirrors your own, but its different enough to reveal previously unseen insights. Wisdom comes from experience. Ovid wrote, The burden becomes light that is shared by love. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
